          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">How I Tested Portfolio Builders</h2>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">Full transparency on my process</p>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              I built <strong>real portfolio sites</strong> across 3 AI builders. Not demo sites—actual portfolios I'd show to clients.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed ml-6 list-disc">
              <li><strong>UX Designer Portfolio:</strong> 12 case studies, 87 photos, smooth scroll animations</li>
              <li><strong>Photography Portfolio:</strong> 150+ high-res images, gallery layouts, proofing gallery</li>
              <li><strong>Illustration Portfolio:</strong> Mixed media, custom hover effects, contact form</li>
